T1  - Punishment from the Manager's Perspective: A Grounded Investigation and Inductive Model
AU  - Butterfield, Kenneth D.
AU  - Trevino, Linda Klebe
AU  - Ball, Gail A.
Y1  - 1996/12/01
PY  - 1996
